# Directory Convention

src/saathy/
├── api.py # FastAPI instance
├── config.py # Pydantic Settings singleton
├── vector/ # Qdrant repository layer
│ └── repository.py
├── scheduler.py # APScheduler init
└── main.py # Gunicorn/Uvicorn entrypoint


* All long-running background jobs live in `scheduler.py`.
* Do **not** create additional sub-packages in Sprint 1.
* `__all__` exports should stay minimal to keep import graph clear.
